{"type":"message","id":"4db2c815","parentId":"9d03c8b6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:53:28.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the session startup sequence as specified in AGENTS.md. I need to read the required files before responding. Let me check what's listed:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — already in Project Context\n2. Read `USER.md` — already in Project Context\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) — today is 2026-03-23, yesterday is 2026-03-22\n4. If in MAIN SESSION: Also read `MEMORY.md` — already in Project Context\n5. Read `CONTEXT.md` — need to check if this exists\n6. Read `memory/active-projects.md` — need to check if this exists\n7. Check for `memory/LAST_SESSION.md` — need to check\n8. Reset persona state\n\nThe project context already includes SOUL.md, USER.md, MEMORY.md, AGENTS.md, BOOTSTRAP.md, IDENTITY.md, TOOLS.md, and HEARTBEAT.md. But I need to read the memory files for today/yesterday and check CONTEXT.md and active-projects.md. I should also check for LAST_SESSION.md.\n\nLet me read the memory files and other required files.","thinkingSignature":"a98145f79db9da3df19ecf37ac2dd275ea8f258b45daf0b6749aee8db8f2a6f0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2vnt6rzz6b1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-23.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2vnt6rzz6b1_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-22.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2vnt6rzz6b1_3","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\CONTEXT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2vnt6rzz6b1_4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\active-projects.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z2vnt6rzz6b1_5","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\LAST_SESSION