{"type":"message","id":"31744358","parentId":"8eb72293","timestamp":"2026-03-23T16:20:30.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Pushed. Now let me update the workspace memory with what happened. The SPARK API is rebuilt, committed, and running on port 8099. The demo mode works without an API key, and the real LLM call works when OPENAI_API_KEY is set.","thinkingSignature":"dac22d73bafb6aa355ad4c78d9d5bf75633346061e67317ea34c7ee4b712b290"},{"type":"text","text":"**SPARK API is back up** — rebuilt from bytecode archaeology, committed and pushed. Running on port 8099.\n\n**What's working:**\n- `GET /health` — health check\n- `GET /creative/tensions` — list all 12 tensions\n- `GET /plans` — rate limit plans\n- `POST /creative/generate` — full drift → tension → generation pipeline\n- `POST /creative/expand` — expand previous output\n- Demo mode (no API key needed) + real OpenAI/Anthropic when keys are set\n- Rate limiting (free: 10/mo, pro: 100/mo via `x-spark-plan` header)\n\n**To use with a real LLM:** `setx OPENAI_API_KEY \"your-key\"` then restart the server.\n\nServer is live at `http://localhost:8099` — docs at `/docs`."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54711,"output":242,"cacheRead":12582,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774282824982}}
