{"type":"message","id":"7723f27e","parentId":"bf3ca2b3","timestamp":"2026-03-23T16:56:41.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach set his OpenAI API key in his permanent system environment variables. The server running in the terminal window might not have picked it up since it was started before the variable was set. He needs to restart the server in that terminal window for it to load the new environment variable.\n\nLet me tell him to restart the server in that terminal (Ctrl+C, then up arrow, enter).","thinkingSignature":"75363ae323cbdf04fc707d6928464dcc380e0e1a016c16f10e115bc4d48da159"},{"type":"text","text":"You'll need to restart the server in that terminal for it to load the new env var. In that terminal window:\n\n1. `Ctrl+C` to stop the current server\n2. Then press **Up Arrow** and **Enter** to restart it\n\nThen try the generate endpoint — it should pick up your key automatically."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":147,"cacheRead":69213,"cacheWrite":192,"totalTokens":69595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774284994250}}
